-steady\nstate models of accretion and the derived chemical composition of asteroidal\ndebris in DBZ white dwarfs.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 30 Apr 2012 20:00:00 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 14 Jun 2012 18:37:30 GMT"}],"update_date":"2012-06-15"}
